                        </p>
                        <div class="skills-tags">
                            <span class="skill-tag">Suite Adobe</span>
                            <span class="skill-tag">Figma</span>
                            <span class="skill-tag">Ergonomie</span>
                            <span class="skill-tag">Accessibilité</span>
                        </div>
